message:
In all professions when working with Human Trafficking Victims we need to remember their needs are what matters not ours. “In a victim-centered approach, the victim's wishes, safety, and well-being take priority in all matters and procedures.”-Office For Victims Of Crime
National Slavery and Human Trafficking Prevention Month #HumanTraffickingAwareness
